Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.17,0:29:21.67,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}フィールドを歌うわ　so futuristic player
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.74,0:29:24.83,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}重なる想い　次の笑顔へ
